Binary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7641276975930797", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8558659074192578"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1730195980, "id": "8590958937629258", "version": "1.01 (3401)", "version_code": 3401, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7641276975930797", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8558659074192578"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1729808894, "id": "8561658390559313", "version": "1.01 (3400)", "version_code": 3400, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7641276975930797", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8558659074192578"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "462418319806168"}]}, "change_log": "Heyhoo Stackers, Patch 1.01 just went live!\n\nThe patch mostly consists of QoL improvements and bug fixes. You can find the complete list here: \n\n[Multiplayer]\n- Added a confirm button to the disconnect flow\n- Pedestal height now works in multiplayer\n- Object no longer stick to your hands after exploding while being held by a client\n- Fixed an issue where repeated connects and disconnects would leave the client believing they were the host\n\n[UI]\n- Height labels are not placed correctly above the pedestal in AR\n- Removed the 'next level' button when completing the final level\n- Added the level index to the title text in-level\n- Fixed an issue with the welcome message\n- Added extra text in the options to let players know that they can Press \"A\" anytime to move the table in AR\n\n[Level]\n- Stopped daily challenge from completing prematurely\n- Daily challenge now uses the player selected measurement system\n- Fixed infinite loading screen when trying to start the daily challenge while having no internet connection\n\n[Objects]\n- Object outlines are now only disabled above the pedestal\n\n[Misc]\n- Removed the Microphone permission check\n- Set a limit on the amount of gizmos can be spawned in the main hub\n- Set a limit on the amount of props can be spawned in the main hub\n- Fixed placement of explosion button and confetti in AR\n\nIf you encounter issues, let us know on our Discord! (discord.gg/DYS2ZpvBfm)\n\nOtherwise, happy Stacking and see you on the leaderboards!\n", "created_date": 1729770838, "id": "8558659074192578", "version": "1.01 (3399)", "version_code": 3399, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}